(103, 1, '2013-12-09 05:03:23', '2013-12-09 05:03:23', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gallery images="105" type="flexslider_fade" grid_style="circle" img_size="full" columns="col3" onclick="link_no" interval="10" show_bullets="true"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][uxb_heading text="Hi, my name is Sally Krivaci" type="h2" has_line="false" icon_size="16"][vc_column_text]People watching has always been one of my favourite pastimes. But more than observing how they look, I''ve long been fascinated with what makes some people happy and successful than others, when their externals might point to them having everything. How do they have such fulfilling lives, with purpose and recognition? What inspires and motivates them? Where are they getting their confidence from? What gives them the strength to deal with everything life thows their way?[/vc_column_text][vc_button title="See our works" href="#" target="_self" size="wpb_regularsize" uxb_icon="icon-caret-right"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][uxb_divider style="special"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][uxb_heading text="How I can help you?" type="h3" has_line="true" icon_size="16" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][vc_column_text]I facilitate and run workshops for women on professional and personal development as part of my business, See us Shine. I also offer one-on-one coaching to help you realise just how amazing you really are. I can assist you in:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>helping you find your true values and live by them</li>\r\n	<li>Confront your unconscious behaviours and old patterns</li>\r\n	<li>Support you through your fears</li>\r\n	<li>Help you to eliminate any negative influences</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nHelp you clarify your goals[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][uxb_heading text="Why I can help you?" type="h3" has_line="true" icon_size="16" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][vc_column_text]In the space of just a few years, I went from being a single 30 year old career woman to a wife and mother of three. Thrust into the demanding domain of parenthood, my interest in people  and particularly those in a similar situation to my own  deepened. Exposed to the challenge of balancing, pleasing everyone and still keeping my needs met, was no easy feat. One day an idea suddenly dawned on me: I want assist other women in understanding the many ways in which they can enrich their lives and reach their full potential.\r\n\r\nWhen Im not working hard assisting people like you, I still enjoy taking time out to observe people and ponder what makes them tick.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][uxb_heading text="Qualifications" type="h3" has_line="true" icon_size="16" css_animation="bottom-to-top"][vc_column_text]\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>The Life Coaching College - <a href="http://www.thelifecoachingcollege.com.au" target="_blank">www.thelifecoachingcollege.com.au</a></li>\r\n	<li>Archetype Academy - <a href="http://archetypeacademy.com.au" target="_blank">http://archetypeacademy.com.au</a></li>\r\n	<li>E-Disc (Extended Disc Accredited Level 2 consultant) - <a href="http://www.extendeddisc.com" target="_blank">http://www.extendeddisc.com</a></li>\r\n	<li>Phillips Institute(Certificate IV in Training and Assessment) - <a href="http://www.phillips.edu.au" target="_blank">http://www.phillips.edu.au</a></li>\r\n	<li>Member of the ABNLP (Australian Board of NLP) - <a href="http://www.abnlp.org.au" target="_blank">http://www.abnlp.org.au</a></li>\r\n	<li>ICF (International Coach Federation) - <a href="http://www.coachfederation.org/" target="_blank">http://www.coachfederation.org/</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][uxb_divider style="special"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][uxb_heading text="From The Blog" type="h3" has_line="true" icon_size="16"][vc_posts_grid grid_categories="28,29,27" grid_teasers_count="4" type="list" g