(258, 1, '2015-02-25 09:36:04', '2015-02-25 09:36:04', 'I dont know about you, but even though were only in the early stages of 2015 Ive heard and read a lot already, that this is going to be the best year yet!\r\n\r\nAnd who wouldnt want that! So how is it going to happen? I always think that when you are in the flow with life you are also in your happiest state (thats usually when good things happen) - and happiness isnt something that just happens to us all the time, its also a choice. Choosing not to do certain things can make this happen as well. So doesnt it just make sense to build new habits to create a better and happier life. Dont we all love the feeling of fulfillment and satisfaction.\r\n\r\nSo, to get started Ive made a list of only a few things I will be doing this year to start me off and I thought I would share them with you. Feel free to do these too, you can add to it or just do your own thing.\r\n\r\nNow, we all know that doing the same things as you did last year will more than likely give you the same results as last year. If you want different results this year, you will have to do different things this year to have different results.\r\n\r\nHave you ever noticed even just doing one simple task differently, can make substantial change, even if we change the way we perceive a situation or problem. When we change the way we look at, or feel about something, you create a more positive feeling and therefore become a happier person. Who doesnt like being around happy people. I know I do!\r\n\r\nSome really easy and simple ways to do this is by:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Gratitude  Yes, being grateful for some of the wonderful things and people in your life can really make the world of difference.</li>\r\n	<li>Connection  Give someone a compliment. Do something for someone without being asked.</li>\r\n	<li>Try new things  Do something different for the first time. Perhaps something youve been wanting to do for a while and immerse yourself in all the positive feelings.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEven just trying these new steps for a few weeks, I know will be of benefit. Why not give it a go  you just might be on your way to have your happiest year yet!', 'How to be a happier You!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-be-a-happier-you', '', '', '2015-02-26 06:33:21', '2015-02-26 06:33:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sally-krivaci/?p=258', 0, 'post', '', 0),
