(294, 1, '2015-02-25 10:37:46', '2015-02-25 10:37:46', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_gallery images="107" type="flexslider_slide" grid_style="circle" img_size="full" columns="col3" onclick="link_no" interval="10" show_bullets="true"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][uxb_heading text="Reconnect with you, prioritise your happiness and set clear boundaries" type="h2" has_line="false" icon_size="16"][vc_column_text]This two day workshop, using NLP activities reconnects you to the most important person <em>YOU</em> and brings you happiness and fulfilment while recharging your batteries. Take a fresh look at life - make time for <em>YOU</em> as no one else will.\r\n\r\nIn this 2 day workshop we will help you:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Feel connected to yourself and others</li>\r\n	<li>Have clear boundaries for yourself and others</li>\r\n	<li>Be confident in your opinions and ideas again</li>\r\n	<li>Prioritise your time and your happiness</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Cost:</strong>\r\n\r\n2 day Workshop - $1,099.00\r\nEarly Bird Special  Pay prior 3 weeks commencement $ 999.00[/vc_column_text][vc_button title="BOOK NOW" target="_self" size="wpb_regularsize" uxb_icon="icon-shopping-cart"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][uxb_divider style="special"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][uxb_heading text="Who is it designed for?" type="h3" has_line="true" icon_size="16"][vc_column_text]The How Many Hats course is designed for the 40 plus woman who is searching for answers, looking for greater impact or experiencing change. You may even be looking for meaning and purpose, not sure where you fit in anymore. Some women may be wanting a better understanding of their emotions and have more control over them. Perhaps, just the need to confidently be involved with life again.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][uxb_heading text="Whats involved?" type="h3" has_line="true" icon_size="16"][vc_column_text]During these 2 days we help you to u